### 4.5 Insights (Blog / Podcasts / Thought‑Leadership)

* Category tabs float above a sub‑grade hero; card layout identical to Home insights.  Posts adopt **IBM Plex Serif** for long reads. ([MathCo][4])

### 4.6 Careers

